 ## Configuration
 Set the following environment variable to enable VirusTotal integration:
 - `VIRUSTOTAL_API_KEY`: Your VirusTotal API Key.
+
+### Hold Integrity Integration
+To enable the **Sync Hold Integrity** button and integration features, you must set the following environment variables:
+- `HOLD_INTEGRITY_API_KEY`: The JWT Bearer token.
+- `HOLD_INTEGRITY_PROJECT_ID`: The Project ID (e.g., `RecentPhishingDomains`).
+
+If these variables are missing, the UI components will be hidden.
